2026-05-18T04:11:25.6089203Z 272        <!--
2026-05-18T04:11:25.6089741Z 273            Same hardening for Glance's InvisibleActionTrampolineActivity.
2026-05-18T04:11:25.6090583Z 274            The library entry is singleInstance with its own taskAffinity
2026-05-18T04:11:25.6091379Z 275            but omits excludeFromRecents (unlike its sibling
2026-05-18T04:11:25.6092167Z 276            ActionTrampolineActivity which already has it). When the
2026-05-18T04:11:25.6093024Z 277            process dies before the trampoline finishes, the system can
