2026-05-18T04:11:25.9397374Z 12    <!--
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9397684Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9397967Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9398567Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9398852Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9399191Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
