2026-05-18T04:11:25.9665874Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9666451Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9666828Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9667180Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-18T04:11:25.9667543Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
